Apple has released iOS 12, and the OS is now available to download on supported Apple devices. For iPhone owers, iOS 12 will run on the iPhone 5s up to the new iPhone Xs and Xr. When checked by MyBroadband, the iOS update was 1.65GB on an iPhone X. Apple said iOS 12 brings a number of improvements to users, including new Photos features, Memoji, Screen Time, and Siri Shortcuts. The new features are listed below.